- âœ… Automatically timestamp when guests are added
- âœ… Toggle RSVP status (Attending/Not Attending)
- âœ… Edit or remove guests dynamically
- âœ… Guest limit set to 10, with alert when exceeded
- âœ… Stylish green buttons for RSVP, Edit, and Remove
- âœ… Responsive layout with Tailwind-style CSS
- âœ… Background party image for immersive experience

